statements: SELECT * FROM event_attendance;
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_date FROM event_attendance WHERE event_id = 1;
SELECT attendee_name, attendee_email, attendee_age FROM event_attendance WHERE attendee_gender = 'Female';
SELECT attendee_name, attendee_location FROM event_attendance WHERE attendee_age > 25;
SELECT event_name, attendee_name, attendee_email FROM event_attendance ORDER BY event_date DESC, attendee_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM event_attendance WHERE attendee_age > 30 ORDER BY event_date DESC, event_name ASC
SELECT attendee_name, attendee_email, attendee_location FROM event_attendance WHERE attendee_gender = 'Male' AND attendee_age >= 25 ORDER BY event_name ASC
SELECT event_name, COUNT(attendee_id) as total_attendees FROM event_attendance GROUP BY event_name HAVING total_attendees > 10 ORDER BY total_attendees DESC
SELECT DISTINCT event_date FROM event_attendance WHERE attendee_gender = 'Female' ORDER BY event_date DESC

SELECT event_name, attendee_name, attendee_email, attendee_location FROM event_attendance WHERE event_date >= '2022-01-01' AND event_date <= '2022-12-31' AND attendee_location IS NOT NULL ORDER BY event_date ASC
SELECT * FROM EventAttendance;
SELECT attendee_id, attendance_status FROM EventAttendance WHERE check_in_time > '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT first_name, last_name, age FROM DemographicInformation WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT * FROM DemographicInformation WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT first_name, last_name, email_address FROM DemographicInformation WHERE occupation = 'Engineer';
SELECT * FROM EventAttendance WHERE attendance_status = 'Present';
SELECT first_name, last_name, gender, age FROM DemographicInformation WHERE age > 25;
SELECT event_id, check_in_time FROM EventAttendance WHERE check_in_time >= '2022-01-01 10:00:00';
SELECT * FROM DemographicInformation WHERE gender = 'Female' AND occupation = 'Engineer';
SELECT attendee_id, first_name, email_address FROM DemjsonraphicInformation WHERE last_name LIKE 'S%';
SELECT * FROM event_attendance;
SELECT event_name, event_date, attendee_name FROM event_attendance ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT attendee_id, age, gender, location, email FROM demographic_information WHERE age > 30;
SELECT strategy_id, target_audience, marketing_channel, budget FROM marketing_strategies WHERE budget > 5000 ORDER BY budget DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_date, attendance_status FROM event_attendance WHERE attendance_status = TRUE ORDER BY event_date;
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_date, attendee_name, attendance_status FROM event_attendance;
SELECT attendee_id, age, gender, location, email FROM demographic_information ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT event_id, event_name, attendee_name, attendance_status FROM event_attendance WHERE attendance_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM marketing_strategies WHERE budget > 1000 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT strategy_id, event_id, target_audience, marketing_channel, conversion_rate, budget FROM marketing_strategies WHERE event_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM events;
SELECT event_name, event_date FROM events ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT a.attendee_name, f.rating FROM attendees a INNER JOIN feedback f ON a.attendee_id = f.attendee_id;
SELECT a.attendee_name, d.location FROM attendees a INNER JOIN demographics d ON a.attendee_id = d.attendee_id WHERE d.gender = 'M';
SELECT event_name, COUNT(attendee_id) AS num_attendees FROM attendees GROUP BY event_name HAVING num_attendees > 5;
SELECT event_name, event_date FROM events;
SELECT attendee_name, age, gender, occupation FROM attendees WHERE age > 30;
SELECT feedback_id, rating, comments FROM feedback WHERE event_id = 1001;
SELECT attendee_name, gender, location, interests FROM attendees JOIN demographics ON attendees.attendee_id = demographics.attendee_id;
SELECT event_name, event_date, attendee_name, rating FROM events JOIN feedback ON events.event_id = feedback.event_id;
SELECT * FROM event_attendance;
SELECT event_name, event_date, attendee_name FROM event_attendance ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT event_name, attendee_name, attendee_email FROM event_attendance WHERE event_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT event_name, attendee_name, attendee_email FROM event_attendance WHERE event_name = 'Music Concert';
SELECT event_name, attendee_name, attendee_email FROM event_attendance WHERE event_id = 123;
SELECT * FROM event_attendance ORDER BY event_date DESC, attendee_name ASC LIMIT 10;

SELECT event_name, attendee_name, event_date, engagement_score FROM event_attendance JOIN event_engagement ON event_attendance.event_id = event_engagement.event_id AND event_attendance.attendee_id = event_engagement.attendee_id WHERE event_attendance.event_id = 100 AND engagement_score > 50 ORDER BY event_date ASC, engagement_score DESC;

SELECT event_name, event_date, attendee_name, gender FROM event_attendance JOIN event_demographics ON event_attendance.attendee_id = event_demographics.attendee_id WHERE gender = 'Male' AND event_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT DISTINCT a.event_name, b.age, b.occupation, b.city, e.engagement_type FROM event_attendance a JOIN event_demographics b ON a.attendee_id = b.attendee_id JOIN event_engagement e ON a.event_id = e.event_id AND a.attendee_id = e.attendee_id WHERE e.engagement_type = 'Survey' AND b.age BETWEEN 25 AND 40 ORDER BY event_date DESC;

SELECT event_name, event_date, feedback_text FROM event_feedback JOIN event_attendance ON event_feedback.event_id = event_attendance.event_id AND event_feedback.attendee_id = event_attendance.attendee_id WHERE event_date >= '2022-03-01' ORDER BY feedback_date ASC;
